Challenge 6

#Creating AIC model 
m <- lm(data = overall, rate ~ log(density) + log(population) + log(gdp_capita) + income)
s <- stepAIC(m, scope = . ~ ., direction = "both")
## Start:  AIC=2030.13
## rate ~ log(density) + log(population) + log(gdp_capita) + income
